Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:18.31,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:29.77,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:36.71,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:47.83,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.77,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:08.66,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:20.54,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:26.38,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:36.18,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:29.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:36.71,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:47.83,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:08.66,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:20.54,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:26.38,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:36.18,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:46.11,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,110)}Ep. 21 - The Man Who Designed Adelaide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, and so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:24.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the goats are also thirsty this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:40.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what happened to your goatling, Sticky?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:45.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see, you're just as worried as I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:47.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It got out through here, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:54.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But where could it be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:09.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, I'll cut the rest of it myself.\NYou go roll them instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:12.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to roll well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... You're a clumsy one. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:23.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't the roll be tighter\Nif I hold it from this end? 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:26.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so. Hold it for me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? What are you up to, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell by looking?\NWe're making bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:38.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you do it without permission,\NDr. Deighton will scold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not if Doctor himself asked us to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:42.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:49.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Lucy-May, I can't find the goatling anywhere.\NSeems like it dug under the fence to fly the coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious, sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:53.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For how long had it been gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:56.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No clue. When I checked just now,\Nit was already missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go look for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:01.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If Mr. Pettywell and his black dog\Ndecide to attack it, it's very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:03.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:04.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming to look for it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:10.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And leaving the bandages half-done, just like that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's irresponsible, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pansy! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pansy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:54.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pansy! Pansy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:57.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:01.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Pansy! Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:08.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That was awfully naughty of you to do! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:15.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine how excited we were\Nto try a salad made from these radishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:18.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And where'd Lucy-May go to look for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:21.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May! Lucy-May! I found it right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:24.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I found this Pansy vermin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And don't eat the plants\Nfrom our field next time, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, Pansy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:39.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goats don't understand a single word\Nof what we humans say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:41.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:44.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta be more attentive, Kate. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to tell Clara, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we keep mum, nobody would have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"Nobody would have a clue," seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:01.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad and mom could tell what's what\Nat the first glance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But they couldn't tell it was Pansy who ate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite the rogue, you know that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:10.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's keep mum!\NAt least with Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:15.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So you found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:15.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:20.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're making me feel like a fool.\NI've finished rolling up all the bandages already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:23.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. And sorry for the trouble, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:27.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know? Pansy never went to the field\Nthat's behind our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:30.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was actually just hiding in the grass over there,\Ncross my heart! 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:36.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, just put Pansy back into the enclosure.\NSee? It won't run away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:36.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:47.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, could you put this hammer\Nback into the toolbox for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And what will you do? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go look at Mr. Mac's burial. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No! Children can't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:54.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're just going to watch secretly from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you coming too, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:06:59.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sis, counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:00.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:01.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How irresponsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:15.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! And what is this little thing doing? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:15.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:19.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:23.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't suppose the funeral is already over, sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:26.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad and the others have been gone for a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Funerals aren't supposed to end so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:30.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But let's step up anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:42.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The funeral of our neighbor Mr. Mac
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:46.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,was held on top of a lonely hill\Non the outskirts of Adelaide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't yet any cemetery to speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:56.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, no pastor either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So we came a bit late, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And who might that man be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The one that approached Mrs. Mac?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:06.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And now he's talking to Mr. Bernard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:12.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll have my leave now.\NAnd please stay strong. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:21.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May! Hurry! If dad notices us,\Nwe'll certainly get scolded!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like we escaped unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The slim man we saw before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:35.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:38.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was Colonel Light!\NColonel William Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The man who designed Adelaide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The Surveyor General of all of Southern Australia! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So that man was Colonel Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:49.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Probably the busiest man in town,\Nhe still bothered to show up for the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:50.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:52.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:58.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly wasn't expecting\Neven Colonel Light to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:59.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You too, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:09:59.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He had just returned from the Barossa Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:05.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To arrive here at this hour,\Nhe had to get up awfully early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the area they're currently surveying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:10.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That area as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:15.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope that man keep doing his best\Nto expedite the surveying process.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:19.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm itching to start cultivating\Nour own plot as soon as possible. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:24.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Some say, that man is currently\Nthe busiest man in all of Southern Australia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:29.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mapping the backwoods and surveying the land\Nboth are immensely time-consuming. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I never understood that before coming here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I must tell you, that man's health\Nis actually deteriorating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He's sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he's been suffering\Nchest pains for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:43.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But in order to fulfill his duties\Nhe denies himself any sleep or rest. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:45.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's just excessive. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Am I free to go play around for the rest of today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:56.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:11:00.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Up to this point, we were constantly\Noverly reliant on your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:02.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get back to work tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:03.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:07.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Fishing, then? However, they don't sell\Nany fishing lines or hooks here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:09.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I brought some with me from England.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:11.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? First time I'm hearing of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not just that, but I chose really good ones. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A remarkable preparedness! 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Should I try around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:48.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, they sprout a lot faster here.\NThe growth is also fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:52.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And the season for sowing seeds\Nis only slightly different from that in England. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:55.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We don't know what winter will be like yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:58.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it's clearly going to be warmer than in Yorkshire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:00.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think the rain is too sparse here? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:01.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's sparse indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:05.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it also could be a seasonal thing\Nand it's only so sparse this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:06.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's been nibbled on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:15.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What could've nibbled on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Lucy-May's hamster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, these footprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:21.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father, those are the goat's footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Too small for a goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The goatling's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:24.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goatling's?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goatling escaped the enclosure earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:31.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That goatling and his mother\Nare our prime concern when it comes to the field. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:35.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara, speaking of which,\Nwhere are Kate and Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:38.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to stop them,\Nbut they went to see the funeral anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? They were there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:44.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But when you all have returned home,\NI thought they should return soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:47.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:48.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:49.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:00.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he went downstream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's upstream for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:04.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think our brother went downstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:06.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was upstream! I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why dontcha go upstream to check, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:09.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, we're going downstream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:28.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:31.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:37.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That was very clumsy, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:39.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't fished out a single one yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:46.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I was hoping I'd finally get to fish\Nall by myself after all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're not here to bother you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:50.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:55.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I know the last time you went fishing\Nwas rightly ages ago! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:58.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To be precise, about five months ago or so,\Nwhen we were still in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the long spell without fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:07.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, maybe the fish in England and in Australia\Nrequire different techniques to catch them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout you call that enough, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:13.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir! We'll watch in silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Such a big fish living here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, pull it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:46.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:49.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't pull it out soon,\Nit'll just run away again! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's still too soon to pull it out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up, Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The line's gonna snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:04.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You should relax it a bit, Ben! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It's big!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:13.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pull it harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Slower! Do it slowly! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:23.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:25.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you lose out to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Relax it a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:28.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right! Relax a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:29.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, now's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:41.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:48.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Rats! 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Your pulling timings are in need of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:55.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was thanks to you chiding in\Nthat I've lost my cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:57.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Well, my apologies if so,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:58.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen you earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:06.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I was also attending Mr. Mac's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:09.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And who exactly were you to poor Mac? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We were neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Your sisters, I reckon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:21.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Kate and Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:23.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, and I am Ben Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:28.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I see you already know who I am,\Nso I guess we can skip the part where I introduce myself. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:35.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:40.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Ben, it's been a truly long while\Nsince I last had a day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,On that occasion, I thought I'd go fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:45.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Fishing here looks promising,\Nif you're good at it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:49.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't exactly say I'm good at it either.\NRather, I'm on the same level as you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:51.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That said, would you allow me to fish here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You got any bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd dig some when I get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, feel free to use my bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You've not a lot of it left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:04.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I need a favor from you two.\NQuickly catch some worms in here, will you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Girls are usually scared of worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:08.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind catching some myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry for these girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:15.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Lucy-May dreams\Nof keeping a worm as a pet one day. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:18.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even for someone like me, a worm\Ndoesn't look like the kind of pet you'd wanna keep. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:24.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You love all kinds of animals,\Nbut worms are an exception? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:27.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not afraid of them either,\Nso I can catch some.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:30.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So be it. And sorry for the trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:36.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please use these worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:37.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:51.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Back when I was six,\NI was taken away from home. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:54.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And when I was twelve, I joined the navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:58.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, I was convinced\Nthat I'm as much a grown-up as I will ever get... 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:02.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But now I see - at twelve, one is still largely a child,\Nhowever you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:06.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Comment: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Too bad, too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:18.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, don't you think this is enough already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:20.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we gather a bit more just in case?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:24.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With this much, those two will be able\Nto treat all the fish in the river to a feast! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:27.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Light must be someone\Nterribly important, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:31.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He was way scarier in my mind,\Nbut it turns out he's actually very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That way! Look over there. But slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Do it from here.\NJust turn your head casually.  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Near the root of that big tree, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:47.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:51.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna catch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:57.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll take these worms now\Nand go give them to brother and Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,On my way back,\NI'll walk to the other side of the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:04.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, you start approaching the rabbit slowly, while looking as unconcerned as you can. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:07.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see! We'll surround it from both sides? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:10.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's important that the rabbit doesn't get a hunch.\NYou got that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:11.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here, your worms!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:44.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:51.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? But that sure is a lot of worms they caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:53.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, now we both gotta catch at least one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:55.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll catch way more. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:20:02.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,From an age of six and until I was twelve,\NI lived in the village of Theberton, in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:04.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Until you joined the navy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:09.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The scenery in these parts\Nis exactly like that in Theberton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You went fishing there as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:13.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I used to fish a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not feeling quite well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:23.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It started way before I came to Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:27.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But this place has an overwhelmingly good climate,\Nso who knows if I don't get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:31.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you could also develop a fever\Nof unknown nature, just like Mr. Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:35.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. The hinterlands here\Nstill harbor all kinds of dangers. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:40.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm a bit older, I want to join the exploration team and go on expeditions to hinterlands all the time. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:42.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you know what it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:47.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Last December, we had three folk die\Non a mission of mapping the estuary of Murray River. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like their boat capsized.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:56.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even to this day, some argue\Nthat rather than building Adelaide here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:21:01.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,we should've founded it near Lake Alexandrina,\Nat the estuary of Murray River.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But this here seems like a great place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:06.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The three that passed away last year
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:10.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,went there to find out whether or not\Nfounding a city there would be viable. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Adelaide is just fine where it is now! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Starting now, Adelaide's expansion\Nis bound to be explosive. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter how much it expands,\Nit will never be a squalid and dirty place. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:24.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been to London? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:25.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:29.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That city is full of places\Nthat are utterly squalid and dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:31.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It had become the focal point for all of Europe. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:35.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Our Adelaide, in turn,\Nis the world's cleanest city. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:37.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Its serenity is second to none. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:40.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm confident that it'll stay this way, Ben. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:44.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:51.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I caught one! I caught it! Look, Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:51.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:53.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did it at last!
Comment: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:11.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:17.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:18.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:43.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.78,0:23:20.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It's a dingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:23.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You brute! It was ours! You thief! 
